{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"478735db7e","title":"工人阶级与民族资产阶级的矛盾是国内的主要矛盾","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"eb0eb28ebe","index":0,"year":1952,"month":6,"day":6,"articleId":"478735db7e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"13560baeec","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"478735db7e","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在中共中央统战部起草的一个文件上的批语。毛泽东同志批判了这个部的负责人把民族资产阶级看作是中间阶级的错误观点。"}],"contents":[{"id":"6fb6caa463","type":"title","text":"工人阶级与民族资产阶级的矛盾是国内的主要矛盾！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"478735db7e"},{"id":"13560baeec","type":"paragraph","text":"在打倒地主阶级和管贷资产阶级以后，中国内部的主要矛盾即是工人阶级与民族资产阶级的矛盾，故不应再将民族资产阶级称为中间阶级。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"478735db7e"}],"page":{"id":"b6aa4aad16","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"478735db7e","start":127,"end":127}}}},"__N_SSG":true}